* NHS internal market, a policy of competition in England&#x27;s National Health Service
* Single market or common market, an association of countries which have removed trade barriers to form continuous market
* United Kingdom Internal Market Act 2020, an act of the UK Parliament to prevent internal trade barriers and restrict the powers of the devolved administrations
